    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292344</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_030_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>シルフ！　&lt;Claus&gt;だ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Sylph! It's me, &lt;Claus&gt;!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292344</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_030_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私のことを覚えているなら、
姿を現してほしい！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If you remember me, please appear before us!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292452</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_030_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>覚えています、&lt;Claus&gt;。
ダオス戦役の折、
ともに戦った勇士</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I remember, &lt;Claus&gt;. I served you during
your heroic fight against Dhaos. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292556</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_030_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>光栄だ。過去のよしみで
頼みを聞いてもらいたいのだが</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It was an honor. As an old comrade, could
you bother to listen to my request?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292648</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_030_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まずは
話を聞きましょう。
何でしょうか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We'll listen to what you have to say. What is it?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292752</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_030_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>我々におまえの精霊晶核を
分けてもらえないだろうか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Would it be too much to ask for
you to lend us your Atomism Core? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292876</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_030_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>精霊晶核を……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Lend you my Atomism Core...? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292876</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_030_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わかりました。
チャンスを与えましょう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I understand, I'll give you this chance.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292988</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_030_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>チャンス？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A chance? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292988</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_030_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>やっぱタダじゃもらえねーの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Won't you just give it to us?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>293200</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_030_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>精霊晶核は、私たち自身の分身、
あるいは卵とも言える
大切なものです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Atomism Core is our innermost, most important
piece. A vital egg for our subsistence.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>293200</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_030_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私たちの風に翻弄されず、
打ち勝つことができれば、
精霊晶核を与えましょう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If you can withstand our wind and strike victorious,
we'll lend you our Atomism Core.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>293280</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_030_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>やっぱり、
また戦うんだ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I knew it...we have to fight again...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>293352</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_030_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よし！　やってやる！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All right! Let's get started!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>293492</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_030_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>来なさい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Come at me!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
